long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Let the spirit of the Dendro Archon, Nahida, light up your new tab. Immerse yourself in her serene beauty and powerful connection to the elements as you explore the wonders of Teyvat. With this dynamic wallpaper, experience the magic of the Sumeru region every time you open a new tab, keeping the Dendro vision close to your heart.

Key Features
🌿 Enchanting Nahida Visuals: Beautiful live wallpaper showcasing the Dendro Archon in her full glory.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Effortlessly search the web while surrounded by the world of Genshin Impact.
🕒 Clock & Date: Stay on top of time with an integrated clock and date feature.
🎯 Customizable Shortcuts: Add and manage shortcuts to access your favorite websites.
🔗 Manage Extensions: "Remove Extension" and "More Extensions" links available in the bottom-left corner.

Let Nahida guide you through Teyvat with every new tab you open. Perfect for fans of Genshin Impact and the magic of the Dendro Archon.
